</p>
</statement>
<solution>
<p><ul><li>4.7947012075297</li></ul></p><p><m>\displaystyle{P}{\left({t}\right)}={750}{e}^{{{0.06}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{1000}={750}{e}^{{{0.06}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle\frac{{1000}}{{750}}={e}^{{{0.06}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{\ln{{\left(\frac{{1000}}{{750}}\right)}}}={0.06}{t}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle\frac{{\ln{{\left(\frac{{1000}}{{750}}\right)}}}}{{0.06}}={t}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{t}={4.7947012075297}</m></p>
</solution>
